      <odd id="aspace_aa61c750c738ebafa195f80d42b3f2f6">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 37 (YRG 37), Records of associations, institutes, centers, and organizations affiliated with Yale University.</p>  
      </odd>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_b51c13601807f218a47afd277a340231">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The records were transferred from the Yale Women's Action Committee, 1993.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_dcdb2eab9f36ac178c667f594f376fee">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>Access to the records is restricted. See Collection Contents for details.</p>
         <p>Some records in this finding aid have been redacted, as they include student names, donor names, and other restricted data. These records will not appear in the published finding aid.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
